      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. every time i see another report about the permafrost melting or the heatwaves it just feels like... why even bother? like we're all just watching a slow motion train wreck and there's nothing anyone can actually do to stop it. it feels so pointless to even plan a future when the world is literally dying.",
